ons she has had with her counterparts in Algeria, Egypt, Libya, Morocco and Tunisia on the decision to end funding for search and rescue missions for migrants in danger of drowning in the Mediterranean; and if she will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Mr Gareth Thomas","212357"
