"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101037","Cabinet Office","false","2014-10-30","<p>The Government Digital Service is working closely with HM Passport Office. The Government is fully committed to protecting public data, including in all aspects of the passport application process.</p><p>In line with the practice of successive administrations, details of internal discussions are not normally disclosed.</p><p> </p>","Horsham","Mr Francis Maude",,"2014-10-30T14:11:14.3441584Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101037/answer","Biography information for Lord Maude of Horsham","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101037/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101037/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-10-27","Passports","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what liaison is taking place between his Department and the Home Office on the (a) design of, (b) structure of and (c) security for the new digital vault for storing and processing digital ID pictures for use in passports; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir Paul Beresford","Mole Valley","Sir Paul Beresford","212034"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101038","Cabinet Office","false","2014-10-30","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p><p> </p>","Reading East","Mr Rob Wilson",,"2014-10-30T14:13:14.6460725Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101038/answer","Biography information for Mr Rob Wilson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101038/answer","PQ 212071 ONS 371.pdf","PQ 212071 ONS 371.pdf","ONS Letter to Member - Minimum Wage","ONS Letter to Member - Minimum Wage","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/101038/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-10-27","Minimum Wage: Brigg","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many (a) full-time and (b) part-time employees in Brigg and Goole constituency were paid the minimum wage in the last year for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Andrew Percy","Brigg and Goole","Andrew Percy","212071"
